## allowed all rescan path use das
EXPLAIN BASIC select /*+leading(a) use_nl(v)*/ sum(a.c1+a.c2+a.c3+a.c4), sum(v.c1+v.c2+v.c3) from t1 a, (
    select c1, c2, c3 from t1 b union all select c3, c2, c1 from t1 c where c1 < 4
) v where a.c2 = v.c1;
Query Plan
========================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                                  |NAME    |
--------------------------------------------------------
|0 |SCALAR GROUP BY                           |        |
|1 |└─PX COORDINATOR                          |        |
|2 |  └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR                    |:EX10000|
|3 |    └─MERGE GROUP BY                      |        |
|4 |      └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN                  |        |
|5 |        ├─PX PARTITION ITERATOR           |        |
|6 |        │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN               |a       |
|7 |        └─SUBPLAN SCAN                    |v       |
|8 |          └─UNION ALL                     |        |
|9 |            ├─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET       |b       |
|10|            └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE RANGE SCAN|c       |
========================================================
